      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken meticulous care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
