    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically pristine example of the A80 chassis. Powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, this vehicle retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and factory-spec wastegate settings. The drivetrain features the robust Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, providing crisp gate engagement and seamless power delivery to the Torsen limited-slip differential. The undercarriage is exceptionally clean, showing no signs of stress on the subframe or corrosion on the double-wishbone suspension components. All factory VIN tags are present on the body panels, and the engine exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders with no forced induction leaks. This is a collector-grade specimen for the enthusiast who values mechanical purity and unmolested engineering.",
